And I will try to tell
to you guys the day

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:33.240
that I realized that I was
not able to play that game.

00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:42.070
12 years ago-- well, let's
go a little bit back,

00:22:42.070 --> 00:22:47.420
when I had been trained
to be a chef in Europe.

00:22:47.420 --> 00:22:50.810
And lots of good
chefs in Europe used

00:22:50.810 --> 00:22:55.490
to plant their own
vegetables, their own herbs.

00:22:55.490 --> 00:22:58.660
And this is so nice.

00:22:58.660 --> 00:22:59.590
I agree with that.

00:22:59.590 --> 00:23:01.100
I love that idea.

00:23:01.100 --> 00:23:04.860
So as a trained
chef, I learned you

00:23:04.860 --> 00:23:10.220
think you can raise
your own ingredients.

00:23:10.220 --> 00:23:16.450
And you can also understand
that the most important moment

00:23:16.450 --> 00:23:21.390
for a chef is not the
service when the guest comes.

00:23:21.390 --> 00:23:25.200
It is the prep, what
we call mise en place.

00:23:25.200 --> 00:23:30.370
If you didn't have a very
well done and organized mise

00:23:30.370 --> 00:23:34.090
en place, you're going to
lose in between the service,

00:23:34.090 --> 00:23:36.520
lose yourself.

00:23:36.520 --> 00:23:42.340
12 years ago, I bought
a huge area in Amazonas.

00:23:42.340 --> 00:23:45.730
The ex-owner in a small
community, local community,

00:23:45.730 --> 00:23:50.530
used to fight because part
of the area, both of them

00:23:50.530 --> 00:23:54.360
believed they owned it.

00:23:54.360 --> 00:23:56.800
When I bought the area,
I bought the problem.

00:23:56.800 --> 00:24:01.050
So I decided to
solve the problem.

00:24:01.050 --> 00:24:02.360
And I went in there.

00:24:02.360 --> 00:24:07.940
I had a one entire afternoon
conversation with the natives.

00:24:07.940 --> 00:24:11.530
And in the end, I made a
very simple proposition.

00:24:11.530 --> 00:24:15.670
I said to them, which
part of the area

00:24:15.670 --> 00:24:16.970
you believe it is yours?

00:24:16.970 --> 00:24:18.370
They said, there, there, there.

00:24:18.370 --> 00:24:23.240
I said, OK, go to the
city, pay the tax,

00:24:23.240 --> 00:24:27.150
and I will never, ever--
and nobody will never, ever

00:24:27.150 --> 00:24:28.330
touch your lands.

00:24:28.330 --> 00:24:31.220
And they made it.

00:24:31.220 --> 00:24:33.695
And I became so proud.

00:24:33.695 --> 00:24:40.410
I started to feel myself the
smartest, coolest, intelligent,

00:24:40.410 --> 00:24:47.970
near to God, really
near, almost beside him.

00:24:47.970 --> 00:24:51.000
And I couldn't play with this.

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:54.770
That area in Amazonas
is a very poor area,

00:24:54.770 --> 00:24:57.560
but is not a miserable area.

00:24:57.560 --> 00:25:01.850
That community, they used
to have lots of kids.

00:25:01.850 --> 00:25:05.670
It was clear that even
if they have food,

00:25:05.670 --> 00:25:08.530
maybe kids were underfed.

00:25:08.530 --> 00:25:10.984
So I decided to
send food to them.

00:25:10.984 --> 00:25:11.900
And I started to send.

00:25:14.860 --> 00:25:18.310
A few months later,
I went to this area.

00:25:18.310 --> 00:25:20.870
To enter in my
area, I might should

00:25:20.870 --> 00:25:26.630
cross the local
community in the area.

00:25:26.630 --> 00:25:29.480
